name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Time Doctor: Workforce Analytics and Time Tracker

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Track time in Chrome with our Browser App.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get started quickly with Time Doctor's browser app. No need to download a separate desktop application. This app works seamlessly within the Chrome web browser and integrates with popular project management tools like Jira, Trello, and Asana. Gain valuable insights into your team's productivity, whether they're remote or working in an office or hybrid working environment.

How it works: https://support.timedoctor.com/knowledge/installing-time-doctor-browser-app
